headline: Concentrix Corporation (CNXC) Q2 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Concentrix (CNXC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.17% and +1.57%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
